---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy | WV Wild Outdoors"
  description="Privacy policy for WV Wild Outdoors website and customer data handling."
>
  <Header />

  <main class="bg-brand-cream min-h-screen py-12 md:py-16">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <article class="max-w-3xl mx-auto bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm p-8 md:p-12">

        <h1 class="font-display font-bold text-3xl md:text-4xl text-brand-brown mb-8">
          Privacy Policy
        </h1>

        <p class="text-stone-500 mb-8">
          Last updated: December 2025
        </p>

        <div class="prose prose-stone max-w-none">

          <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-xl text-brand-brown mt-8 mb-4">
            Information We Collect
          </h2>
          <p class="text-stone-600 mb-4">
            WV Wild Outdoors is a local retail store. We do not sell products online.
            When you visit our website, we may collect:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-stone-600 mb-6 space-y-2">
            <li>Basic analytics data (pages visited, general location, device type) through Cloudflare Analytics</li>
            <li>Email address if you voluntarily subscribe to our newsletter</li>
            <li>Information you provide through contact forms</li>
          </ul>

          <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-xl text-brand-brown mt-8 mb-4">
            How We Use Your Information
          </h2>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-stone-600 mb-6 space-y-2">
            <li>To respond to inquiries submitted through our contact forms</li>
            <li>To send newsletter updates if you've subscribed</li>
            <li>To understand how visitors use our website and improve it</li>
          </ul>

          <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-xl text-brand-brown mt-8 mb-4">
            In-Store Purchases
          </h2>
          <p class="text-stone-600 mb-4">
            For in-store firearm purchases, we are required by federal law to collect
            certain information for ATF Form 4473 and conduct NICS background checks.
            This information is:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-stone-600 mb-6 space-y-2">
            <li>Collected only at time of purchase in our physical store</li>
            <li>Required by federal law for firearm transactions</li>
            <li>Stored securely according to ATF regulations</li>
            <li>Never sold or shared except as required by law</li>
          </ul>

          <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-xl text-brand-brown mt-8 mb-4">
            Cookies and Tracking
          </h2>
          <p class="text-stone-600 mb-4">
            Our website uses minimal tracking. We use Cloudflare Analytics, which is
            privacy-focused and does not use cookies to track individual visitors.
          </p>

          <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-xl text-brand-brown mt-8 mb-4">
            Third-Party Services
          </h2>
          <p class="text-stone-600 mb-4">
            We use the following third-party services:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-stone-600 mb-6 space-y-2">
            <li><strong>Cloudflare:</strong> Website hosting and analytics</li>
            <li><strong>Web3Forms:</strong> Contact form processing</li>
            <li><strong>Buttondown:</strong> Newsletter management (if you subscribe)</li>
          </ul>

          <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-xl text-brand-brown mt-8 mb-4">
            Your Rights
          </h2>
          <p class="text-stone-600 mb-4">
            You may:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-stone-600 mb-6 space-y-2">
            <li>Unsubscribe from our newsletter at any time</li>
            <li>Request information about what data we have about you</li>
            <li>Request deletion of your data (except where retention is required by law)</li>
          </ul>

          <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-xl text-brand-brown mt-8 mb-4">
            Contact Us
          </h2>
          <p class="text-stone-600 mb-4">
            If you have questions about this privacy policy or your data, contact us at:
          </p>
          <address class="not-italic text-stone-600 mb-6">
            <p><strong>WV Wild Outdoors</strong></p>
            <p>121 Birch River Rd</p>
            <p>Birch River, WV 26610</p>
            <p>Phone: (304) 649-2607</p>
          </address>

          <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-xl text-brand-brown mt-8 mb-4">
            Changes to This Policy
          </h2>
          <p class="text-stone-600 mb-4">
            We may update this policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page
            with an updated revision date.
          </p>

        </div>
      </article>
    </div>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>
